# Chiikize 🐾

Keep your little friend alive!

Chiikize is a short virtual-pet-style browser game where the player must care for a character by clicking before its needs run out. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript as a front-end development project.

**Play here:**  
https://praesepe-44.github.io/chiikize/

## Features

- Simple virtual pet gameplay
- Real-time stat management
- Browser-based with no installation required
- Character-focused design

## Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Skills Demonstrated

- DOM manipulation
- Event handling
- Timers and game loops
- Conditional logic
- Front-end web development fundamentals

## Goal

Keep your character Biba happy and alive for as long as possible!

## Running the Project

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/praesepe-44/chiikize.git
   ```

2. Open `index.html` in your preferred web browser.

